nov]], [[Aleksei Serebryakov (actor)|Aleksey Serebryakov]] || Crime ||\n|-\n| '''''[[First on the Moon]]'''''  || '''''\u041f\u0435\u0440\u0432\u044b\u0435 \u043d\u0430 \u041b\u0443\u043d\u0435''''' || [[Aleksey Fedorchenko]] || Aleksei Anisimov || [[Mockumentary]] ||\n|-\n| '''''[[The Italian (2005 film)|The Italian]]'''''  || '''''\u0418\u0442\u0430\u043b\u044c\u044f\u043d\u0435\u0446''''' || [[Andrei Kravchuk]] || Kolya Spiridonov || Drama ||\n|-\n| '''''[[Hunting for Asphalt]]'''''  || '''''\u041e\u0445\u043e\u0442\u0430 \u043d\u0430 \u0430\u0441\u0444\u0430\u043b\u044c\u0442\u0435''''' || || || Drama ||\n|-\n| '''''[[Last Weekend (2005 film)|Last Weekend]]'''''  || '''''\u041f\u043e\u0441\u043b\u0435\u0434\u043d\u0438\u0439 \u0443\u0438\u043a-\u044d\u043d\u0434''''' || [[:ru:\u0421\u0430\u043d\u0430\u0435\u0432, \u041f\u0430\u0432\u0435\u043b \u0412\u043b\u0430\u0434\u0438\u043c\u0438\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0438\u0447|Pavel Sanayev]] || [[Ivan Stebunov]], [[Tatyana Arntgolts]] || Thriller ||\n|-\n| '''''[[The Master and Margarita (miniseries)|The Master and Margarita]]'''''  || '''''\u041c\u0430\u0441\u0442\u0435\u0440 \u0438 \u041c\u0430\u0440\u0433\u0430\u0440\u0438\u0442\u0430''''' || [[Vladimir Bortko]] || [[Anna Kovalchuk]], [[Aleksandr Galibin]], [[Oleg Basilashvili]], [[Vladislav Galkin]], [[Sergey Bezrukov]] || Fantasy, drama ||TV miniseries, based on the [[Master and Margarita|book of the same name]] by [[Mikhail Bulgakov]]\n|-\n| '''''[[Order (film)|Order]]'''''  || '''''\u0417\u0430\u043a\u0430\u0437''''' || [[Vera Glagoleva]] || [[Nataliya Vdovina]], [[Aleksandr Baluev]] || Drama ||\n|-\n| '''''[[Shadowboxing (2005 film)|Shadowboxing]]'''''  || '''''\u0411\u043e\u0439 \u0441 \u0442\u0435\u043d\u044c\u044e''''' || [[Aleksei Sidorov]] || [[Denis Nikiforov]], [[Yelena Viktorovna Panova|Yelena Panova]], [[Andrey Panin]] || Sport drama ||\n|-\n| '''''[[The State Counsellor (film)|The State Counsellor]]'''''  || '''''\u0421\u0442\u0430\u0442\u0441\u043a\u0438